You can get a PhD in
less than six years.

00:26:07.200 --> 00:26:08.000 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:09.640 align:middle line:84%
>>HOLECEK: So if you
attain lucidity--

00:26:09.640 --> 00:26:12.010 align:middle line:84%
and this is why I think what
