00:26:12.010 --> 00:26:14.770 align:middle line:90%
I completely stand behind it--

00:26:14.770 --> 00:26:17.210 align:middle line:84%
potentially, these nocturnal
meditations, in fact,

00:26:17.210 --> 00:26:19.390 align:middle line:84%
represent the pedagogy
of the future.

00:26:19.390 --> 00:26:22.720 align:middle line:84%
Once the induction
