00:26:28.000 --> 00:26:30.830 align:middle line:84%
phenomenological techniques,
first-person meditative

00:26:30.830 --> 00:26:31.630 align:middle line:90%
techniques.

00:26:31.630 --> 00:26:33.568 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Can you train
