00:26:35.860 --> 00:26:36.610 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:26:36.610 --> 00:26:38.610 align:middle line:84%
And that is, in fact,
what makes lucid dreaming,

00:26:38.610 --> 00:26:42.080 align:middle line:84%
