yoga, an actual practice.

00:26:42.080 --> 00:26:45.550 align:middle line:84%
So there's a whole battery
of both Eastern and Western

00:26:45.550 --> 00:26:49.090 align:middle line:84%
approaches that you can
use to not only increase

00:26:49.090 --> 00:26:53.420 align:middle line:84%
your recollection of
dream, but the incidence

00:26:53.420 --> 00:26:57.200 align:middle line:84%
