incidences of hyper lucidity.

00:26:57.200 --> 00:26:59.870 align:middle line:84%
And then eventually, that
even matures into lucidity

00:26:59.870 --> 00:27:01.745 align:middle line:90%
in the deep dreamless state.

00:27:01.745 --> 00:27:03.620 align:middle line:84%
And this is where this
material transitions--

00:27:03.620 --> 00:27:06.260 align:middle line:84%
I didn't get to the fifth
of the nocturnal practices.

00:27:06.260 --> 00:27:08.510 align:middle line:84%
This is a purely
Tibetan contribution.

00:27:08.510 --> 00:27:11.180 align:middle line:84%
The fifth one is
called Bardo yoga.

00:27:11.180 --> 00:27:14.390 align:middle line:84%
Bardo is a Tibetan word
very similar to liminal that

00:27:14.390 --> 00:27:17.450 align:middle line:84%
basically, if you believe in
this sort of thing, refers

00:27:17.450 --> 00:27:20.960 align:middle line:84%
to the gaps between lives,
between incarnations.

00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:23.780 align:middle line:84%
And so therefore, the
fruition of all these

00:27:23.780 --> 00:27:25.820 align:middle line:84%
practices-- and
in fact, somewhat

00:27:25.820 --> 00:27:30.800 align:middle line:84%
in the kind of lens of Hegel,
this Hegelian notion of

00:27:30.800 --> 00:27:34.670 align:middle line:84%
transcend but include,
each succeeding practice

00:27:34.670 --> 00:27:37.170 align:middle line:84%
transcends but includes
its predecessor,

00:27:37.170 --> 00:27:39.770 align:middle line:84%
which means Bardo
yoga transcends what

00:27:39.770 --> 00:27:42.200 align:middle line:84%
includes sleep yoga, dream
yoga, lucid dreaming,

00:27:42.200 --> 00:27:43.560 align:middle line:90%
and liminal dreaming.

00:27:43.560 --> 00:27:46.850 align:middle line:84%
And so the great gift here is
that these practices, according

00:27:46.850 --> 00:27:49.610 align:middle line:84%
especially to the Tibetan
view, can radically

00:27:49.610 --> 00:27:51.230 align:middle line:90%
help you prepare for death.

00:27:51.230 --> 00:27:55.460 align:middle line:84%
And this is even suggested in
Western intellectual thought.

00:27:55.460 --> 00:27:58.820 align:middle line:84%
I mean, Thanatos, the
Greek god of death,

00:27:58.820 --> 00:28:03.990 align:middle line:84%
Hypnos, the Greek god of sleep,
they're not just brothers.

00:28:03.990 --> 00:28:05.370 align:middle line:90%
They're twins.

00:28:05.370 --> 00:28:07.380 align:middle line:84%
So there's a very
intimate connection

00:28:07.380 --> 00:28:09.700 align:middle line:84%
between sleeping,
dreaming, and dying.

00:28:09.700 --> 00:28:12.520 align:middle line:84%
And so what the Tibetans do--
and there are others as well.

00:28:12.520 --> 00:28:14.670 align:middle line:84%
The Islamic tradition has
a dream yoga tradition.

00:28:14.670 --> 00:28:17.100 align:middle line:84%
I've been in contact
with Islamic scholars.

00:28:17.100 --> 00:28:19.320 align:middle line:90%
The Jewish tradition--

00:28:19.320 --> 00:28:20.937 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Dying is
like lucid dreaming.

00:28:20.937 --> 00:28:23.020 align:middle line:84%
>>HOLECEK: Dying is very
much like lucid dreaming.

00:28:23.020 --> 00:28:24.960 align:middle line:84%
And so as I mentioned
earlier, not only

00:28:24.960 --> 00:28:28.410 align:middle line:84%
do we have this bidirectional
thing where lucid dreaming can

00:28:28.410 --> 00:28:31.980 align:middle line:84%
lead to lucid living, well,
it's actually tridirectional,

00:28:31.980 --> 00:28:34.950 align:middle line:84%
which means lucid dreaming
can lead to lucid dying.

00:28:34.950 --> 00:28:37.020 align:middle line:84%
It's what we started
talking about at the outset.

00:28:37.020 --> 00:28:40.470 align:middle line:84%
Conscious dreaming can lead to
conscious dying, because you're

00:28:40.470 --> 00:28:43.650 align:middle line:84%
working arguably, according
to these wisdom traditions,

00:28:43.650 --> 00:28:46.200 align:middle line:84%
with the same
dimensions of mind.

00:28:46.200 --> 00:28:48.910 align:middle line:84%
And so therefore, if you can
attain lucidity-- in fact,

00:28:48.910 --> 00:28:51.660 align:middle line:84%
in the great Tantric traditions
of what's called the Nyingma

00:28:51.660 --> 00:28:52.890 align:middle line:90%
school--

00:28:52.890 --> 00:28:55.860 align:middle line:84%
if you contain lucidity--
it's an archetypal number.

00:28:55.860 --> 00:28:58.620 align:middle line:84%
They say seven times, but we're
not to take it too literally.

00:28:58.620 --> 00:29:00.630 align:middle line:84%
It just means with
some constancy.

00:29:00.630 --> 00:29:03.090 align:middle line:84%
What they argue is that
the same proficiency

00:29:03.090 --> 00:29:05.640 align:middle line:84%
you develop in the
nighttime dream

00:29:05.640 --> 00:29:08.220 align:middle line:84%
then extends into the
dream at the end of time.

00:29:08.220 --> 00:29:10.860 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, you can have
a lucid, conscious dying

00:29:10.860 --> 00:29:13.140 align:middle line:84%
experience where you
maintain awareness

00:29:13.140 --> 00:29:15.533 align:middle line:84%
throughout the entire
death trajectory.

00:29:15.533 --> 00:29:16.950 align:middle line:84%
And this is where
the great-- this

00:29:16.950 --> 00:29:18.420 align:middle line:84%
is a little bit of
a sidebar topic,

00:29:18.420 --> 00:29:20.820 align:middle line:84%
but this is where the great
texts like the Tibetan

00:29:20.820 --> 00:29:23.640 align:middle line:84%
Book of the Dead come
from, the great masters who

00:29:23.640 --> 00:29:26.310 align:middle line:84%
maintain lucidity who can
actually come back like travel

00:29:26.310 --> 00:29:30.760 align:middle line:84%
guides and basically share what
they experienced in that space.

00:29:30.760 --> 00:29:32.820 align:middle line:84%
Well, we have the same
mind as the Buddha.

00:29:32.820 --> 00:29:35.460 align:middle line:84%
We have the same mind
as these great masters.

00:29:35.460 --> 00:29:36.930 align:middle line:90%
We just need to train it.

00:29:36.930 --> 00:29:38.190 align:middle line:90%
We just need to cultivate it.

00:29:38.190 --> 00:29:42.030 align:middle line:84%
And that's why this is not just
rhetoric or metaphysical mumbo

00:29:42.030 --> 00:29:43.050 align:middle line:90%
jumbo.

00:29:43.050 --> 00:29:44.423 align:middle line:90%
This is a pedagogical approach.

00:29:44.423 --> 00:29:45.590 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's the real deal.

