00:30:20.400 --> 00:30:21.775 align:middle line:84%
there's a difference
between what

00:30:21.775 --> 00:30:24.480 align:middle line:84%
philosophers call
access consciousness

00:30:24.480 --> 00:30:26.430 align:middle line:90%
and phenomenal consciousness.

00:30:26.430 --> 00:30:29.010 align:middle line:84%
What that means is you can
